CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Nocturne - Stepping out in traditional style, the AKA Sorority, Iota Chapter, sponsored its annual Autumn Nocturne for freshmen and other members of the student body at Pitt, Saturday, Oct. 6. - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of nine women, members of Alpha Kappa Alpha, Iota Chapter Sorority, posed in front of stage with curtain decorated with leaves, for Autumn Nocturne dance, another version
